## 1. Brand name and taglines (exact strings)

### Written name
- Always **Pehchaan Careers** (capital **P**, capital **C**). Never `pehchaan careers`, `PEHCHAAN`, or `Pehchaan careers` as the formal brand string.

### Taglines by context
| Context | Exact string | Notes |
|--------|----------------|--------|
| English (site + tools topbar) | `Your identity. Your path.` | Second line under **Pehchaan Careers** in tool chrome. **Do not** replace this line with a tool title or step label; put tool context in the hero chip, H1, or body. |
| Hindi (footer motto, tools) | `Aapki pehchaan, aapki raah.` | Lowercase **a** after period in Hindi line as shown. |
| Marketing site footer tagline | Same Hindi line in `.footer-tagline` | Keep in sync with tools. |

Other taglines (Hindi alternates, manifesto lines) live in `Pehchaan_Careers_Brand_Guide.md` §2 — use only where that document or product explicitly allows (e.g. decks, social), not as random substitutes in headers/footers.

---

## 2. Logos, icons, favicons, and brand mark

### Canonical asset files (repo root `assets/`)
| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `assets/pehchaan_logo_light.svg` | **Marketing site** header + footer wordmark on dark footer / light contexts. |
| `assets/pehchaan_logo_dark.svg` | Dark-background marketing / print-style placements. |
| `assets/pehchaan_icon.svg` | **Site `<link rel="icon">`** on `index.html` (and preferred for any new static page that can use a path to `assets/`). |
| `assets/pehchaan_logo_light.png`, `assets/pehchaan_logo_dark.png`, `assets/pehchaan_icon.png` | Raster fallbacks / social; prefer SVG on web. |

### Logo usage rules
- **No distortion:** preserve aspect ratio; do not squash the wordmark or icon.
- **Contrast:** dark logo variants on light surfaces; light logo on dark nav/footer (`index.html` header uses dark gradient — use **light** logo there as today).
- **Clear space:** treat ~1× the cap-height of “P” in **Pehchaan** as minimum breathing room where practical.
- **Colours in the mark:** do not recolour the official logo files for “theme experiments.” Programme-approved tints (e.g. opacity overlays on hero decorations) are not the same as editing logo artwork.

### Tool chrome: inline mark (40×40 “sun + paths”)
Standalone HTML tools use a **rounded square** (`border-radius: 12px` at 40×40), **background `#085041`** (teal dark), containing the **inline SVG** that matches the brand mark (amber sun arc + rays, teal converging paths). **Gold reference:** `Tools/pehchaan_stream_advisor.html` (`.topbar-logo svg`) or `parent-faq/components/PehchaanToolChrome.tsx` (`LogoSvg`). When updating the mark, **update all copies in lockstep** (static tools + `PehchaanToolChrome`) or extract to one shared asset/CSS once the repo introduces a shared bundle.

### Favicon policy
- **`index.html`:** `assets/pehchaan_icon.svg` (type `image/svg+xml`).
- **`Tools/pehchaan_*.html`:** Many use a **data-URI SVG** favicon echoing teal-dark + amber + paths — acceptable if colours **exactly** match tokens (`#085041`, `#EF9F27`, `#1D9E75`). Prefer **either** data-URI **or** `../assets/pehchaan_icon.svg` for consistency when touching `<head>`; avoid unrelated emoji or generic globe icons.
- **Next/export apps:** set favicon to the same artwork/filename pattern as siblings.

### Alt text
- Logo images: `alt="Pehchaan Careers"` or `alt="Pehchaan Careers logo"` (descriptive, consistent).
- Decorative icons (inline SVG beside nav): `aria-hidden="true"` when paired with visible text; **social** icons need `aria-label` / `title` as on the marketing footer.

